      "description": "Rate of VSR view changes over time. Each view change represents a leader election.\n\nFrequent view changes indicate cluster instability:\n- Network partitions between nodes\n- Node crashes or restarts\n- High load causing timeouts\n\nA healthy cluster should have zero view changes during normal operation. Occasional spikes during planned maintenance are expected.",
