      },
      "description": "The latest committed operation number for each node. This shows replication progress across the cluster.\n\nAll nodes should have similar op numbers. Divergence indicates:\n- Replication lag (replica behind)\n- Network partition (nodes in different views)\n- Node recovery in progress\n\nThe slope indicates write throughput - steeper means more operations being committed.",
      "fieldConfig": {
